<L>__{interior gideon's hotel room night}
<C>__{tex}
<D>__{ but sneakin' in there on your own that a way, why, man, you was bound to get yore tokus kicked. i mean, what'd you think he'd do walk up 'n' shake you by that hand o' yores?}
